name: fileNumber
description: File number (must be set to FFFF when the extended file number is used (bytes 18-20)

name: scanTypeNumber
description: Scan type number (must be set to FF when the extended channel set number is used (bytes 16-17)

name: firstTimingWordInteger
description: First timing word integer; Timing word for first sample if multiplexed. Multiply by sample skew time (byte 11) and baseScanInterval (general header 1) for actual time

name: traceHeaderExtension
description: Number of 32-byte trace header extension blocks (maximum 15)

name: sampleSkew
description: Sample skew (see First timing word, byte 7)
